<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Paiement réussi</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .success-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .success-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            font-size: 50px;
        }
        
        .success-title {
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .btn-return {
            background-color: #3a56d4;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .btn-return:hover {
            background-color: #2a46c4;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(58, 86, 212, 0.3);
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <div class="success-card">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="success-title">Paiement réussi !</h1>
            
            <p class="text-muted">Merci pour votre achat. Votre paiement a été traité avec succès.</p>
            
            <p>Vous recevrez prochainement un email de confirmation avec tous les détails de votre formation.</p>
            
            <a href="{{ path(formations_route) }}" class="btn-return">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i> Retour aux formations
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



